dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c0104dadcfa1732dc194adc7ea6dd5816d36c98f","tid":1809354,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:35:40.000Z","msg":"港共自己都係行人隧道做文宣 我地點解唔可以？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfscZFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfscZFL.jpg&h=778acf14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>18區區議會</strong></ins><br />\n每區區議會需在該區人流就多既位置，<strong>安裝正式既連農文宣牆 (情況有如廣告箱)，</strong> <br />\n同時安排保安公司管理。 費用就香港人既錢(公帑)支付。<br />\n<br />\n以上工程，由黃色工程公司負責，當中可請手足full / part time幫手。<br />\n對家用呢重方法玩咗廿幾年，今次到香港人！<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>[不同政見，都可以提交文宣]</strong></ins><br />\n機會平等，所有人都可以將文宣交到當區區議員手上<br />\n佢地會有既定「機制」去分類放上連農<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>我地要好好理用手上 區議會權力同資源</ins></strong><br />\n- 18-1區文宣正式化<br />\n- 擴大及鞏固黃色經濟圈<br />\n- 支援手足 保護手足<br />\n<br />\n「18區議會入」港共自己都係行人隧道做文宣 我地點解唔可以？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1813044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1813044</a>"},{"pid":"15a9ef0ecab69f20b17c3c6417291b7fe43a8b81","tid":1809354,"uid":112495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f81d5872c938b27ffbeed3a1724161a706a15ca","tid":1809354,"uid":237627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5db022382be984c28a0a8836a847e9bb909719","tid":1809354,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ef67b17bf62612f9c88a2ec1ea8da4bcc0ecf58c","tid":1809354,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:32:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d868faea6ca8017129c004ae4afaa061a8c23e7b","tid":1809354,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"雖然睇法有啲出入 但都會幫推!<br />\n-------------------<br />\n[行動]文宣都十八區開花 A4 label周圍貼 (更新:大量現成圖 即print 即貼!)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aqhhjnU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aqhhjnU</a>"},{"pid":"c1f2e19919895464a32c9ca0f411f8a6dfb2ddf5","tid":1809354,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T01:39:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d7adc0c7ffb7f7fb70d2880e417f89a9fb1ed22","tid":1809354,"uid":112495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2114fee30fa2b12e88355bd4ef327de3c1c4338e","tid":1809354,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"港共自己都係行人隧道做文宣 我地點解唔可以？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfscZFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfscZFL.jpg&h=778acf14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>18區區議會</strong></ins><br />\n每區區議會需在該區人流就多既位置，<strong>安裝正式既連農文宣牆 (情況有如廣告箱)，</strong> <br />\n同時安排保安公司管理。 費用就香港人既錢(公帑)支付。<br />\n<br />\n以上工程，由黃色工程公司負責，當中可請手足full / part time幫手。<br />\n對家用呢重方法玩咗廿幾年，今次到香港人！<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>[不同政見，都可以提交文宣]</strong></ins><br />\n機會平等，所有人都可以將文宣交到當區區議員手上<br />\n佢地會有既定「機制」去分類放上連農<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>我地要好好理用手上 區議會權力同資源</ins></strong><br />\n- 18-1區文宣正式化<br />\n- 擴大及鞏固黃色經濟圈<br />\n- 支援手足 保護手足<br />\n<br />\n「18區議會入」港共自己都係行人隧道做文宣 我地點解唔可以？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1813044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1813044</a>"},{"pid":"d845fe164d55189cc05d59b855c7fd9f32ea2dd8","tid":1809354,"uid":223675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"其實一早有人搵左區議員講呢個議題,得出既結論有以下幾點<br />\n1.連儂牆而家唔係唔合法,拉都係告持有攻擊性武器<br />\n2.驚起左大台<br />\n3.責任問題,連儂牆上面既內容會造成法律責任,<br />\n如:某賣白粉起家既日報,就算明知係真,但係冇證據證明係真都有機會俾人告,要告幅牆,咁邊個負責,如果合法化,咁幅牆既持有人係政府,政府係唔會俾呢樣野發生。<br />\n4.連儂牆本意<br />\n-連儂牆本身係各有各貼,如果有規管,呢個文宣唔貼得,<br />\n果個唔貼得咁本意去左邊呢?<br />\n<br />\n咁當然我咁講得就唔會淨係破壞唔建設<br />\n其實區議員可以同手足合作,咁點合作呢?<br />\n同一時間係果區租場搞大型展覽<br />\n至於展覽d咩就大家心中有數<br />\n人手問題?<br />\n可以請手足幫手管理<br />\n撥款俾手足幫手搞展覽<br />\n純粹個人意見"},{"pid":"088952a893047e029c09754fc0789d5f51fadfb2","tid":1809354,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7841b43251537ba7782842754141a23a8b9d8b94","tid":1809354,"uid":112495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b20f6a066dca66183eb6474887d243fc886a26","tid":1809354,"uid":264138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:32:35.000Z","msg":"[同我簽咗佢]香港十八區居民要求各區議會，設立恆常的議程去回應社區聯署的聯署聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1795969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1795969</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8f214d7e4dbda43594187862759b818a472e7fe1","tid":1809354,"uid":112495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"區議會議員加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c84a88bf1decc47047cecdcc8072dafb02793d","tid":1809354,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc